article_title: Air strikes kill at least 15 in Gaza and reports of a hostage deal being 'close'
sentence: The  Palestinian  news  agency  Wafa  is  reporting  that  at  least  15  people  have  been  killed  in  overnight  air  strikes  on  the  Nuseirat  refugee  camp  and  the  city  of  Khan  Younis  in  the  south  of  Gaza.
